title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Jul 30 2021

description:
PODCAST SUMMARY HOUR 3:


Clay and Buck welcome syndicated radio talk show host Jesse Kelly to chat about Democrats' covid power grab and never-ending mandates. Coronavirus is the greatest thing that ever happened to Dr Fauci. Vegas mask mandate goes against the whole meaning of Las Vegas. C&B take on superhero movies. Rand Paul breaks down Delta variant numbers. Normalize being normal.
